imdb.plot outline: The independently produced show aired for the first time spring 2012. From modest beginnings, and a project group of just three people, the show now has a large team of experts working hard behind the scene, a loyal New York audience and very strong international following. 'On Deck with Lucy' is THE entertainment show when it comes to the 3 T's of NY. Filmed in the city, it highlights the Talent, the Trends and the Tastes of New York. Viewers can see up-close-and-personal interviews with New York celebrities, artists and successful entrepreneurs, take part in competitions and get involved in future shows. It offers a portal to the New York experience for international fans, a valuable reference source for visitors, and a great way of getting closer to the city they love for New Yorkers.
